==English==

===Hyphenation===
:fe&middot;ver

===Noun===
{{en-noun-reg}}

# A higher than normal [[temperature]](1) of a [[person]] (or generally a [[mammal]]). Usually caused by disease:
#:''"I have a '''fever'''.  I think I caught a cold."''

